Package com.karusmc.xmc.core

Provides essential classes built upon Spigot's command handling system that all other packages and classes in this toolkit depend on.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CommandMapObserver
    Observer used by the default CommandMapProxy implementation.
    Dispatcher
    This interface is used by the classes in this toolkit to denote that it delegates execution to subcommands.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CommandManager
    This class acts as a facade and abstracts the internals of the toolkit.
    CommandMapProxy
    Acts as a proxy for the Spigot Server instance's internal CommandMap implementation.
    ConfigurableCommand
    Acts as a base command class for extension by other classes in the toolkit.
    XMCommand
    Acts as a base command class for extension by other classes in the toolkit.

Package com.karusmc.xmc.core Description

Provides essential classes built upon Spigot's command handling system that all other packages and classes in this toolkit depend on. The package includes the base command classes for extension, a command map proxy for the server and a command manager class that provides a high-level facade of the toolkit internals.
